Login Registration System

A C++ console-based application that allows users to register and log in securely. User credentials are stored using file handling, enabling persistent account management.

Features

User Registration

User Login Authentication

File Handling for Data Storage

Input Validation

Simple Console Interface


Technologies Used

C++

Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

File Handling


How to Run

1. Compile the source code using a C++ compiler.


2. Run the executable.


3. Register a new account or log in with existing credentials.


4. Follow the on-screen instructions.



Project Objective

This project demonstrates the implementation of user authentication, file handling, and basic security concepts in C++.
